Block -> { Declset Stmtset }
Declset -> Declset Decl | Decl
Decl -> int Vars ; | bool Vars ;
Vars -> id | Vars , id
Stmtset -> Stmt | Stmtset ; Stmt
Stmt -> Assn
Assn -> id := Arith | id := Comp | id := Cond
Arith -> Term | Arith + Term | Arith - Term
Term -> Factor | Term * Factor
Factor -> id | num | ( Arith )
Comp -> Arith = Arith | Arith > Arith | Arith < Arith
Cond -> Comp -> Arith : Arith 